<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Welcome! Your Subscription is Active</h1>
    
    <p>Dear <%= @customer.name %>,</p>
    
    <p>Thank you for subscribing to <strong><%= @subscription.name %></strong>! Your subscription is now active and ready to use.</p>
    
    <h2>Subscription Details</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Service:</strong> <%= @subscription.name %></li>
      <li><strong>Reference Number:</strong> <%= @subscription.reference_number %></li>
      <li><strong>Amount:</strong> KES <%= @subscription.amount %> per <%= billing_frequency_text(@subscription.billing_frequency) %></li>
      <li><strong>Status:</strong> <%= @subscription.status.capitalize %></li>
      <% if @subscription.current_period_start.present? %>
        <li><strong>Current Period:</strong> <%= @subscription.current_period_start.strftime('%B %d, %Y') %> - <%= @subscription.current_period_end.strftime('%B %d, %Y') %></li>
      <% end %>
      <% if @subscription.next_billing_date.present? %>
        <li><strong>Next Billing Date:</strong> <%= @subscription.next_billing_date.strftime('%B %d, %Y') %></li>
      <% end %>
      <% if @subscription.trial_days.to_i > 0 && @subscription.is_trial? %>
        <li><strong>Trial Period:</strong> <%= @subscription.trial_days %> days (ends <%= @subscription.trial_ends_at&.strftime('%B %d, %Y') %>)</li>
      <% end %>
    </ul>
    
    <p>You can manage your subscription, view invoices, and update payment methods from your dashboard.</p>
    
    <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
    
    <p>Welcome aboard!</p>
  </body>
</html>

